{"tha-ap138:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap138:0.2":"Sobhitavagga ","tha-ap138:0.3":"Campakapupphiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap138:1.1":"“Kanikaramva jotantam, ","tha-ap138:1.2":"nisinnam pabbatantare; ","tha-ap138:1.3":"Obhasentam disa sabba, ","tha-ap138:1.4":"osadhim viya tarakam. ","tha-ap138:2.1":"Tayo manavaka asum, ","tha-ap138:2.2":"sake sippe susikkhita; ","tha-ap138:2.3":"Kharibharam gahetvana, ","tha-ap138:2.4":"anventi mama pacchato. ","tha-ap138:3.1":"Putake satta pupphani, ","tha-ap138:3.2":"nikkhittani tapassina; ","tha-ap138:3.3":"Gahetva tani nanamhi, ","tha-ap138:3.4":"vessabhussabhiropayim. ","tha-ap138:4.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap138:4.2":"yam pupphamabhiropayim; ","tha-ap138:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap138:4.4":"nanapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap138:5.1":"Ekunatimsakappamhi, ","tha-ap138:5.2":"vipulabhasanamako; ","tha-ap138:5.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap138:5.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap138:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap138:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap138:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap138:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma campakapupphiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap138:8.1":"Campakapupphiyattherassapadanam chattham. "}